<p><b>( * ) LÆ°u Ã½ :</b>  XÃ©t <strong>D<sub>B</sub></strong> cÃ³ Ä‘Æ°á»ng Ä‘áº¿n nÃºt <strong>G</strong>, mÃ  nÃºt <strong>G</strong> Ä‘Ã£ á»Ÿ trong <strong><em>queue</em></strong> rá»“i ta so sÃ¡nh giÃ¡ (cost) vá»›i <strong>G</strong> trong <strong><em>queue</em></strong>. Äuá»ng Ä‘i qua <strong>D -&gt; G</strong> (tá»•ng lÃ  75) nhá» hÆ¡n so vá»›i Ä‘Æ°á»ng Ä‘i qua <strong>C -&gt; G</strong> (95) nÃªn ta cáº­p nháº­t giÃ¡ (cost) vÃ  nÃºt cha cá»§a <strong>G</strong>.</p>

<p><strong>=&gt; ÄÆ°á»ng Ä‘i : S -&gt; A -&gt; B -&gt; D -&gt; G</strong></p>

